# Credentials for the AI Translations E2E suite (Playwright).
# Copy this file to `.env.testing` and fill in the values. `.env.testing` is
# gitignored — never commit real secrets. See `e2e/README.md` for where each
# value comes from.
#
# Quote any value containing `#`: dotenv treats an unquoted `#` as the start of an
# inline comment and silently truncates the value (e.g. PASSWORD="…#…").

# --- Provider API keys (all optional) ---
# The matrix runs one parallel lane per key that is set; missing/empty keys are
# skipped, so a partially-filled file tests exactly the providers you have.
OPENAI=
GEMINI=
DEEPL=
CLAUDE=

# --- Fixture project (all required) ---
E2E_PROJECT_CMA_TOKEN=
E2E_DASHBOARD_EMAIL=
E2E_DASHBOARD_PASSWORD=
E2E_PROJECT_ID=
E2E_PROJECT_SUBDOMAIN=

# --- Optional ---
# Only if the dashboard account has 2FA enabled:
# E2E_DASHBOARD_TOTP_SECRET=
# Pin the per-run id used in forked env names (auto-generated from unix-seconds
# when unset); handy in CI or to re-attach cleanup to a crashed run's envs:
# E2E_RUN_ID=
